ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 221, New Brunswick
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 221 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the Minister to provide financial assistance to the province of NEW BRUNSWICK, with respect to the flooding that occurred from April 16 to May 4, 2019.
